Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" < 0 THEN 'A: <0%' WHEN "%1" < 10 THEN 'B: 0-10%' WHEN "%1" < 20 THEN 'C: 10-20%' WHEN "%1" <= 30 THEN 'D: 20-30%' ELSE CASE WHEN NOT "%1" IS NULL THEN 'E: >30%' END END

Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Company Products" <= 3 THEN 'A: 0-3' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Company Products" <= 6 THEN 'B: 4-6' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Company Products" <= 10 THEN 'C: 7-10' WHEN NOT "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Company Products" IS NULL THEN 'D: >10' END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" < 0 THEN 'A: <0' WHEN "%1" < 1000 THEN 'B: 0-1K' WHEN "%1" < 10000 THEN 'C: 1K-10K' WHEN "%1" < 100000 THEN 'D: 10K-100K' WHEN "%1" <= 1000000 THEN 'E: 100K-1M' ELSE CASE WHEN NOT "%1" IS NULL THEN 'F: >1M' END END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Contact Outstanding Balance" < 0 THEN 'A: <0' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Contact Outstanding Balance" < 1000 THEN 'B: 0-1K' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Contact Outstanding Balance" < 10000 THEN 'C: 1K-10K' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Contact Outstanding Balance" < 100000 THEN 'D: 10K-100K' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Contact Outstanding Balance" <= 1000000 THEN 'E: 100K-1M' ELSE CASE WHEN NOT "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Contact Outstanding Balance" IS NULL THEN 'F: >1M' END END

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" < 0 THEN 'A: <0' WHEN "%1" < 5000 THEN 'B: 0-5K' WHEN "%1" < 50000 THEN 'C: 5K-50K' WHEN "%1" < 500000 THEN 'D: 50K-500K' WHEN "%1" <= 2000000 THEN 'E: 500K-2M' WHEN "%1" IS NULL THEN 'Unspecified' ELSE 'F: >2M' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Household Outstanding Balance" < 0 THEN 'A: <0' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Household Outstanding Balance" < 5000 THEN 'B: 0-5K' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Household Outstanding Balance" < 50000 THEN 'C: 5K-50K' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Household Outstanding Balance" < 500000 THEN 'D: 50K-500K' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Household Outstanding Balance" <= 2000000 THEN 'E: 500K-2M' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Household Outstanding Balance" IS NULL THEN 'Unspecified' ELSE 'F: >2M' END

LogicalColumn.name: Customer Acquisition %
LogicalColumn.Description: This is the rate at which you acquire new customers(based on Customer Start Date)

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" = 0 THEN NULL ELSE 100.0d * "%2" / "%1" END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Active Customer History"."# Active Customers" = 0 THEN NULL ELSE 100.0d * "Core"."Fact - CRM - Acquired Customer"."# Customers Acquired" / "Core"."Fact - CRM - Active Customer History"."# Active Customers" END

LogicalColumn.name: # Contacts with Assets Range
LogicalColumn.Description: Ranges based on # Contacts with Assets

Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IS NULL OR "%1" <= 49 THEN 'A: 0-49' WHEN "%1" <= 149 THEN 'B: 50-149' WHEN "%1" <= 299 THEN 'C: 150-299' WHEN "%1" <= 499 THEN 'D: 300-499' ELSE 'E: 500+' END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Contact Assets" IS NULL OR "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Contact Assets" <= 49 THEN 'A: 0-49' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Contact Assets" <= 149 THEN 'B: 50-149' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Contact Assets" <= 299 THEN 'C: 150-299' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Contact Assets" <= 499 THEN 'D: 300-499' ELSE 'E: 500+' END

LogicalColumn.Description: # Households by asset managers

Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Company Assets" IS NULL OR "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Company Assets" <= 99 THEN 'A: 0-99' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Company Assets" <= 199 THEN 'B: 100-199' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Company Assets" <= 299 THEN 'C: 200-299' WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Asset Manager Company Assets" <= 399 THEN 'D: 300-399' ELSE 'E: 400+' END

LogicalColumn.name: # Active Assets
LogicalColumn.Description: This is the count of assets (Insurance Policies/ Financial Accounts) that are still active in the specified period. This column will only show the assets owned for a particular product when the Product column is used in the query.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ASSET_D"."END_DT" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END

LogicalColumn.name: # Active Assets Across all Products
LogicalColumn.Description: This column will always give total number of active assets owned by the customer regardless of the Product selected in the query.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: SUM("Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."# Active Assets Across all Products")

LogicalColumn.name: Total # New Assets Last Month
LogicalColumn.Description: This column calculates the number of new assets (accounts) opened by the cusomter in the last month.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprTextDesc: COUNT(DISTINCT "Core"."Fact - CRM - Asset"."Total # New Assets Last Month")

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_MONTH , "%1", CURRENT_DATE ) < 2 THEN "%2" END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN TIMESTAMPDIFF( SQL_TSI_MONTH , "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ASSET_D"."START_DT", CURRENT_DATE ) < 2 THEN "Oracle Data Warehouse"."Catalog"."dbo"."W_ASSET_D"."ROW_WID" END
